'''益西彭措堪布'''（{{lang-en|Khenpo Yeshe Phuntsok}} {{bd|1971年|||}}）<ref>{{cite web|title=堪布益西彭措仁波切简介|url=http://www.xianmifw.com/guru_yxpc/guru_intro.html|website=Introduction to Khenpo Yeshe Phuntsok Rinpoche|access-date=2016-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012224348/http://www.xianmifw.com/guru_yxpc/guru_intro.html|archive-date=2016-10-12|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，原籍[[四川省|四川省]][[阿坝州|阿坝州]][[壤塘县|壤塘县]]宗科乡。1978至1983年，圆满汉文小学课程后，着重学习[[藏文|藏文]]，1985年考入四川省藏文学校。1986年秋，来到色达喇荣五明佛学院圣地<ref>{{cite web|title=Larung Gar Buddhist Academy|url=https://archive.org/details/LarungGarBuddhistAcademy|website=Moving Image Archive > Spirituality & Religion > Community Spirituality & Religion|publisher=Internet Archive | accessdate=Jan 14, 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Larung Gar Five Sciences Buddhist Academy|url=http://www.tricycle.com/portfolio/larung-gar-five-sciences-buddhist-academy|website=Tricycle-Magazine-Winter 2013|publisher=Tricycle|accessdate=Jan 14, 2015|archive-date=2015-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151126104526/http://www.tricycle.com/portfolio/larung-gar-five-sciences-buddhist-academy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Speaker Series: Contemporary Tibetan Buddhist Meditation in China with Khenpo Sodargye |url=http://www.uvacontemplation.org/content/speaker-series-contemporary-tibetan-buddhist-meditation-china-khenpo-sodargye |website=University of Virginia |publisher=UVaContemplative Sciences Center |accessdate=Jan 15, 2015 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120053200/http://www.uvacontemplation.org/content/speaker-series-contemporary-tibetan-buddhist-meditation-china-khenpo-sodargye |archivedate=2015-01-20 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The hillside homes of Tibetan Buddhists in Larung Gar|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/worldnews/10145659/The-hillside-homes-of-Tibetan-Buddhists-in-Larung-Gar.html?frame=2601701|website=The Telegraph-News-Gallaries-World News|publisher=The Telegraph|accessdate=Jan 14, 2015|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111232948/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/picturegalleries/worldnews/10145659/The-hillside-homes-of-Tibetan-Buddhists-in-Larung-Gar.html?frame=2601701|dead-url=no}}</ref>，师从大恩根本上师法王如意宝[[晋美彭措堪布|晋美彭措堪布]]，得受众多显教经论、密教续部窍诀等传承。自从被法王上师任命为堪布后，即担负起部分教务，培育藏族僧才长达九年。1996年起受法王委托致力于汉僧教学。

至今堪布仍常住学院教化四众弟子，倡导学修“[[菩提心|菩提心]]”“[[般若|般若]]”“[[净土|净土]]”“[[道次第|道次第]]”“[[弥勒五论|弥勒五论]]”等显密教法，创建了显密学会。其中包括修心班，道次第班，净土班，净土高级班，弥勒五论班，般若班，般若讲研班，导归极乐班，观修班。

